Package: dttsp 
Architecture: any
Depends: libfftw3-3, mime-support, liblo7, libc6-i686, gawk, libjack-jackd2-0, jackd2
Recommends: sdr-shell (>= 4.0)
Suggests: usbsoftrock
Description: The core of a Software Defined Radio (SDR) transceiver
 DttSP implements the basic modulation, demodulation, signal conditioning, 
 and synchronization processes required to operate a high performance transceiver
 using DSP as the detection and synthesis stages. 
 sdr-core a standalone program designed to allow the software construction of 
 transceivers for AM, FM, SSB, CW, ... 
